1130
01:11:22,864 --> 01:11:23,990
Hubert Dreyfus.

1131
01:11:24,532 --> 01:11:26,367
Senator,
thank you for joining us.

1132
01:11:26,534 --> 01:11:28,244
<i>Hello, Pat.
Mr. Sellars.</i>

1133
01:11:28,327 --> 01:11:30,621
